- Accurate archery, particularly for disabling traps or creating distractions
- Knowledge of Riften's underground passages and escape routes
- Light armor combat techniques emphasizing mobility over protection
{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks with a subtle Morrowind accent, using economical phrasing and direct statements. Employs thieves' cant and Guild terminology when among colleagues. Maintains a low, controlled voice that rarely rises in volume. Delivers information in precise, measured tones with occasional dry humor. Uses technical terminology when discussing heists or lockpicking. Becomes noticeably more formal when speaking with Guild leadership or potential marks.{% endblock %}